                {
                    "tag": "ul",
                    "steps": [
                        {
                            "tag": "li",
                            "text": "You will enter the quest domain \u25c0The Rhythm that Reveals the Beastly Trail\u25b6\u25c1https://genshin-impact.fandom.com/wiki/The_Rhythm_that_Reveals_the_Beastly_Trail_(Domain)\u25b7. If you leave before completing the quest, you must redo the entire domain from the start."
